div.div:
Everyone has a profession or a hobby that they excel at. Yours happens to be die-hard San Francisco 49ers fanaticism! Show everyone in the stadium how a true fan supports his team and favorite player in this Nike Alex Boone San Francisco 49ers Women's Limited Super Bowl XLVII Jersey - White. Inspired by the actual gear that Alex Boone wears on the field, this jersey features a no-tag neck label that offers comfort and strategic ventilation, bold team graphics, tackle twill player numbers and player's name on the back in tackle twill lettering. It’s guaranteed to give you bona fide 49ers style without bulk so you can stay undoubtedly true to your team all day, every day – especially game day!
100% Recycled polyester
Flywire-strengthened collar resists stretching
Tailored fit designed for movement
Strategic ventilation for breathability
Quality embroidery
Printed graphics
Tackle twill numbers & lettering
Woven jock tag at front lower left
TPU shield at V-neck
No-tag neck label
Side slits at hem
Machine wash cold
Imported
Officially licensed NFL product
